replies.author: youyihj
replies.txt_content:
用<ore:tongxian>
矿辞前面要有ore
还有你这个矿辞名过于迫真，应该用<ore:wireCopper>

replies.author: TRLWeiss
replies.txt_content: 使用<ore:wireCopper>比较好，不加ore前缀可能gg
